    "PhotoViewPicker returns permanently authorized URIs -- no READ_IMAGEVIDEO permission needed for picker-only flows",
    "CameraManager/CameraInput require ohos.permission.CAMERA; getCameraManager via camera.getCameraManager(context) Stage model only",
    "ImagePacker.packing() is deprecated from API 13 -- use packToData() or packToFile() instead",
    "ImageReceiver and all Image Kit instances (ImageSource, PixelMap, ImagePacker) require explicit release()",
    "fileIo operates in app sandbox only; use context.filesDir as base path",
    "photoAccessHelper.getAssets() with picker-returned URIs bypasses READ_IMAGEVIDEO permission",
    "All 8 requested APIs found in local docs; no APIs are missing"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

{
  "module": "08-phone.md",
  "group": "08 -- Phone & Contacts",
  "apiCount": 5,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "call.makeCall",
      "purpose": "跳转到系统拨号界面并显示待拨出号码",
      "anchor": "callmakecall7",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "call.dial",
      "purpose": "直接拨打电话（API 9起废弃，仅系统应用可申请权限）",
      "anchor": "calldial",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "contact (contacts API)",
      "purpose": "联系人管理，包括添加/删除/更新/查询联系人等",
      "anchor": "ohoscontact-联系人",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.telephony.call",
      "purpose": "呼叫管理模块，提供拨打电话、跳转拨号界面、获取通话状态等功能",
      "anchor": "ohostelephonycall-拨打电话",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.contacts",
      "purpose": "联系人管理模块",
      "anchor": "ohoscontact-联系人",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "call.dial 自 API 9 起废弃，普通应用应使用 call.makeCall 跳转到系统拨号界面代替",
    "call.makeCall 仅支持在 UIAbility 中调用，API 12 起新增带 context 的重载支持后台调用（需权限）",
    "call.answerCall / hangUpCall / rejectCall 需系统级权限，普通应用不可用",
    "实际模块名为 @ohos.contact（非 @ohos.contacts），导入路径为 @kit.ContactsKit，导入名为 contact",
    "API 10 起所有 contact 接口需传入 Context 参数（Stage 模型）"
  ],
